---
title: Shawarma-Style Veggie Bowls with Protein Shreds and Yellow Rice
description: Tonight we've got vegetarian shawarma 'on the rocks'! Shawarma-spiced shreds are a smoky and sweet match for earthy yellow rice, tangy olives and juicy baby tomatoes. Tahini sauce and hot sauce provide a delicious finishing touch!
